---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Privacy Policy | CoverToday Insurance" description="CoverToday Insurance Agency privacy policy.">
  <section style="padding-top:48px"><div class="wrap" style="max-width:780px">
    <h1 style="font-size:34px">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="lead" style="margin-top:14px">CoverToday Insurance Agency respects your privacy. This page summarizes how we handle your information.</p>
    <div style="margin-top:24px;color:var(--muted);font-size:16px;line-height:1.7">
      <p><strong>Information we collect.</strong> When you request a quote or contact us, we collect details you provide (name, phone, email, ZIP, and information needed to quote your insurance).</p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px"><strong>How we use it.</strong> Solely to prepare quotes, place coverage, and serve you as your insurance broker. <strong>We never sell your information.</strong></p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px"><strong>SMS.</strong> If you text us or opt in, we may send service messages. Reply STOP to opt out. See our SMS Terms for details.</p>
      <p style="margin-top:14px"><strong>Contact.</strong> Questions? Call (310) 299-5555 or email info@covertoday.com. DOI License #0K77310.</p>
    </div>
  </div></section>
</Base>
